responses.3: New application for your job on Startuply
responses.4: To Whom it May Concern: I am very interested in working at your company. The widgets you make are AMAZING, and I would love to be a part of it. I have many skills, but the most important ones are my abilities to collect information from people, screen it effectively, select the right options, and follow through with the right options quickly. Plus, I even know what to do with the options we did not select. Adding me to your team means saving time, saving money and getting back to doing the work you love doing.
